<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="icon" href="data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox='0 0 100 100'><text y='0.9em' font-size='90'>🥭</text></svg>">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/landing.css">
    <title>Privacy Policy - MangoBridge</title>
    <style>
        .policy-container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 50px;
            /* box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15); */
        }

        .policy-header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .policy-header h1 {
            color: #7678ed;
            font-size: 42px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .policy-header p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .policy-section {
            margin-bottom: 35px;
        }

        .policy-section h2 {
            color: #3d348b;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .policy-section p {
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .back-link {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #7678ed;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .back-link:hover {
            color: #3d348b;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .policy-container {
                padding: 30px 20px;
                margin: 20px;
            }

            .policy-header h1 {
                font-size: 32px;
            }

            .policy-section h2 {
                font-size: 20px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="landing-page">
    <div class="landing-container">
        <div class="policy-container">
            <a href="/" class="back-link">← Back to Home</a>
            
            <div class="policy-header">
                <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
                <p>Last Updated: April 2026</p>
            </div>

            <div class="policy-section">
                <h2>1. Information Collection</h2>
                <p>
                    MangoBridge is committed to protecting your privacy. We do not collect personally identifiable information such as your name, contact number, physical address, email address, or payment information, unless you explicitly provide it to us through account registration or profile settings.
                </p>
                <p>
                    We do collect product usage data to improve our multilingual work platform. This consists of non-personally identifiable information that relates to how you use MangoBridge, including but not limited to: features accessed, time spent using the application, translation language preferences, meeting participation patterns, and any technical errors or issues encountered. This minimal data collection is essential to enhance the functionality of our platform and improve your collaborative experience across language barriers.
                </p>
                <p>
                    By using the MangoBridge website or mobile application, you consent to the collection of this anonymized usage data.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="policy-section">
                <h2>2. Use of Information</h2>
                <p>
                    The non-personally identifiable product usage data we collect serves the sole purpose of improving MangoBridge's multilingual collaboration features. We analyze this data to:
                </p>
                <p>
                    • Understand usage patterns and optimize translation accuracy<br>
                    • Identify and resolve technical issues<br>
                    • Enhance user interfaces for better cross-cultural communication<br>
                    • Refine meeting summary generation and calendar integration<br>
                    • Improve overall user experience across all platform features
                </p>
                <p>
                    The aggregated, de-identified data that we collect cannot be used to personally identify any individual user, ensuring the utmost protection of your privacy while helping us build a better multilingual workplace tool.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="policy-section">
                <h2>3. Data Security</h2>
                <p>
                    While no digital platform can guarantee absolute security, MangoBridge implements industry-standard security measures to protect your information. We employ encryption, secure authentication protocols, and regular security audits to safeguard your data.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Your messages, translations, meeting summaries, and calendar events are stored securely using encrypted databases. Access to this information is strictly limited to authorized personnel who require it for platform maintenance and support purposes.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="policy-section">
                <h2>4. Data Sharing and Third Parties</h2>
                <p>
                    MangoBridge does not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third parties. We may share anonymized, aggregated data for research or analytical purposes, but such data will never contain personally identifiable information.
                </p>
                <p>
                    We use trusted third-party services for essential platform functions such as cloud storage, translation services, and infrastructure. These partners are contractually obligated to maintain the confidentiality and security of your data and may only use it for the specific purposes we authorize.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="policy-section">
                <h2>5. Your Rights and Control</h2>
                <p>
                    You have the right to access, modify, or delete your personal information at any time through your account settings. You may also request a complete export of your data or permanent account deletion by contacting our support team.
                </p>
                <p>
                    If you have concerns about how your information is being used or wish to opt out of certain data collection practices, please reach out to us at the contact information provided below.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="policy-section">
                <h2>6. International Data Transfers</h2>
                <p>
                    As a multilingual work platform serving users globally, MangoBridge may transfer and process your data in countries other than your own. We ensure that such transfers comply with applicable data protection laws and that your information receives adequate protection regardless of where it is processed.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="policy-section">
                <h2>7. Policy Changes</h2>
                <p>
                    Our Privacy Policy may be updated periodically to reflect changes in our practices or legal requirements. Any significant changes will be communicated through the platform, and the "Last Updated" date at the top of this page will be revised accordingly. We encourage users to review this Privacy Policy regularly to stay informed about how we protect your information.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="policy-section">
                <h2>8. Contact Us</h2>
                <p>
                    If you have any questions, concerns, or requests regarding our privacy practices or this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
                </p>
                <p>
                    <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:legal@mangobridge.com" style="color: #7678ed;">legal@mangobridge.com</a><br>
                    <strong>Support:</strong> <a href="mailto:support@mangobridge.com" style="color: #7678ed;">support@mangobridge.com</a>
                </p>
                <p>
                    Please note: By continuing to use MangoBridge, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agree to this Privacy Policy and our practices regarding data collection and usage.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>